Apache v2.4.18 configuration file : 

<VirtualHost *:80>
  ...
  <Directory />
    Options FollowSymLinks
    AllowOverride None
  </Directory>

  <Directory /usr/share>
    AllowOverride None
    Require all granted
  </Directory>

  <Directory /var/www/html/>
    Options Indexes FollowSymLinks
    AllowOverride None
    Order allow,deny
    allow from all
  </Directory>
  ...
</VirtualHost>


# note => config file located in /etc/apache2/apache2.conf

Tutorials sources :
1. http://askubuntu.com/questions/292968/apache2-forbidden-you-dont-have-permission-to-access-dir-on-this-server
2. https://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=1204863
